148
00:10:45,278 --> 00:10:48,157
Not yet. Uh, but
I'm sorry, gentlemen.

149
00:10:48,181 --> 00:10:50,159
There's work to be done
here, so if you'll excuse me.

150
00:10:50,183 --> 00:10:51,761
Let me know if there's
anything we can do.

151
00:10:51,785 --> 00:10:53,362
Anything at all.

152
00:10:53,386 --> 00:10:56,732
And, Steve...
Steve, give me a call.

153
00:11:08,701 --> 00:11:10,013
You got any leads?

