00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:57,147
gonna walk through
that door over there.

258
00:17:00,953 --> 00:17:01,953
One.

259
00:17:03,723 --> 00:17:05,367
Two.

260
00:17:05,391 --> 00:17:07,224
Three.

261
00:17:08,194 --> 00:17:09,760
Four.

