00:29:39,678 --> 00:29:41,723
Look in my eye.

550
00:29:41,747 --> 00:29:43,157
You see the gratitude there?

551
00:29:43,181 --> 00:29:45,993
But I am not doing any more
private investigative work.

552
00:29:46,017 --> 00:29:48,997
Tyler, all I wanted to do is
advance you a little money.

553
00:29:49,021 --> 00:29:51,632
I'm not doing any more PI work.

554
00:29:51,656 --> 00:29:53,334
I happen to have
a check right here.

555
00:29:53,358 --> 00:29:54,903
I'm out of that game.

556
00:29:54,927 --> 00:29:57,839
See the check?

557
00:29:57,863 --> 00:29:59,975
What's the case?

558
00:29:59,999 --> 00:30:02,043
Linda Coolidge
was laid to rest today

559
00:30:02,067 --> 00:30:04,045
in her hometown
of Utica, New York.

560
00:30:04,069 --> 00:30:05,513
There were no services,

561
00:30:05,537 --> 00:30:08,549
and only her mother and her
sister were at the gravesite,

562
00:30:08,573 --> 00:30:11,219
which is the way Linda
would have wanted it.

563
00:30:11,243 --> 00:30:14,455
She was, at heart, a
very private person.

564
00:30:14,479 --> 00:30:17,180
It's hard to believe she's gone.

565
00:30:18,717 --> 00:30:21,529
We'll be right back with
Dr. Farnsworth and the weather,

566
00:30:21,553 --> 00:30:24,520
and Bill Tucker
with sports after this.

567
00:30:25,324 --> 00:30:26,623
Touching tribute.

568
00:30:28,060 --> 00:30:29,671
You didn't like her?

569
00:30:29,695 --> 00:30:32,361
Oh, I did. But he didn't.

570
00:30:33,565 --> 00:30:35,776
Ultimately.

571
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:36,880
Excuse me.

572
00:30:39,137 --> 00:30:40,415
Mr. White? Yes?

573
00:30:40,439 --> 00:30:42,284
Hi, I'm Charlene Matlock.

574
00:30:42,308 --> 00:30:45,220
Our firm is handling
Steve Emerson's defense.

575
00:30:45,244 --> 00:30:48,022
I was wondering if I could
ask you a few questions

576
00:30:48,046 --> 00:30:49,624
about Linda Coolidge.

577
00:30:49,648 --> 00:30:51,592
Is there somewhere
we could go talk?

