I don't have time right now.

580
00:30:57,356 --> 00:30:58,766
Could I make an appointment?

581
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:01,035
Look, I'm sorry, but
my attorney told me

582
00:31:01,059 --> 00:31:03,304
not to get involved with this.

