00:36:56,147 --> 00:36:57,859
I got rained on at the beach.

704
00:36:57,883 --> 00:36:59,694
I'll see you all in the morning.

705
00:36:59,718 --> 00:37:01,462
Where's Emerson?

706
00:37:01,486 --> 00:37:03,431
He was at the TV station
yesterday afternoon.

707
00:37:03,455 --> 00:37:05,733
Doing what? Some investigating.

708
00:37:05,757 --> 00:37:07,535
I told him to stay out of sight.

709
00:37:07,559 --> 00:37:09,169
Well, actually,

710
00:37:09,193 --> 00:37:11,105
I was rather impressed
with what he was doing.

711
00:37:11,129 --> 00:37:13,074
He was getting Linda's
financial records,

712
00:37:13,098 --> 00:37:15,243
going over news footage
of the murder scene.

713
00:37:15,267 --> 00:37:16,778
You were?

714
00:37:16,802 --> 00:37:17,812
Were what?

715
00:37:17,836 --> 00:37:19,080
Impressed?

716
00:37:19,104 --> 00:37:20,448
Yes, I was.

717
00:37:20,472 --> 00:37:24,084
Were you impressed when
I told him stay at his hotel?

718
00:37:24,108 --> 00:37:26,287
Did you consider I might
have had a reason for that?

719
00:37:26,311 --> 00:37:28,022
Well, he was getting results.

720
00:37:28,046 --> 00:37:29,857
I saw no point in stopping him.

721
00:37:29,881 --> 00:37:31,125
Charlene, one of the reasons

722
00:37:31,149 --> 00:37:33,061
I charge my clients
so much money

723
00:37:33,085 --> 00:37:34,995
is so they'll do
what I tell 'em.

724
00:37:35,019 --> 00:37:36,930
This man is a
target for the press.

725
00:37:36,954 --> 00:37:39,100
We can get that
same information.

726
00:37:39,124 --> 00:37:40,468
When are you seeing him again?

727
00:37:40,492 --> 00:37:41,769
We're meeting in the dining room

728
00:37:41,793 --> 00:37:43,070
at his hotel tonight

729
00:37:43,094 --> 00:37:45,206
so I can get some
background on Linda Coolidge.

730
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,696
You find him attractive.

731
00:37:47,599 --> 00:37:49,444
So does most of America.

732
00:37:49,468 --> 00:37:50,967
You're his lawyer.

733
00:37:52,871 --> 00:37:54,415
Are you insinuating

734
00:37:54,439 --> 00:37:56,350
that I might let any
personal feelings

