00:37:56,374 --> 00:37:57,818
I have about a client

736
00:37:57,842 --> 00:37:59,954
interfere with my
professional relationship?

737
00:37:59,978 --> 00:38:02,123
I haven't said anything.

738
00:38:02,147 --> 00:38:03,157
Yet.

739
00:38:03,181 --> 00:38:04,613
Good.

740
00:38:06,351 --> 00:38:08,729
Any luck getting in to
see the boyfriend? Um...?

741
00:38:08,753 --> 00:38:10,731
Lockwood. Yeah.

742
00:38:10,755 --> 00:38:13,434
No. He wouldn't
return my phone calls.

743
00:38:13,458 --> 00:38:16,292
So I... made an appointment
under another name.

744
00:38:17,495 --> 00:38:18,539
That's very devious.

745
00:38:18,563 --> 00:38:20,841
