you might approve.

746
00:38:20,865 --> 00:38:22,610
I'll see you later. Yeah.

747
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:27,515
Yes, ma'am?

748
00:38:27,539 --> 00:38:28,649
Put him on.

749
00:38:31,075 --> 00:38:32,642
Speaking.

750
00:38:34,646 --> 00:38:36,980
